{"tid":2307224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"SAVE 12快閃西門町","createTime":"2020-12-01T04:54:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T15:28:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba129f1553378f43533c795b75418da7b312f33","tid":2307224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:54:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/WPLSRZKZANFXDDTN6C4BYIJ57M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FWPLSRZKZANFXDDTN6C4BYIJ57M%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=cbcb7db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FWPLSRZKZANFXDDTN6C4BYIJ57M%2F&h=5708178a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/WPLSRZKZANFXDDTN6C4BYIJ57M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\nSAVE 12快閃西門町<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VhWjnNZGjR0llIUkRRFECGbTLwQ=/1890x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WX3SRQIBLJCPRHHCJCTMWNB2WE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVhWjnNZGjR0llIUkRRFECGbTLwQ%3D%2F1890x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWX3SRQIBLJCPRHHCJCTMWNB2WE.jpg&h=606ece4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■數名在台港人昨晚在西門町舉「SAVE 12」燈牌，聲援12港人。<br />\n<br />\n昨日是12港人被拘押在深圳第100日，一群在台香港青年昨晚在西門町舉出「SAVE 12」燈牌聲援。不少路人駐足觀看，有人在便利貼上留言聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n途人聲援字句貼滿紙船<br />\n<br />\n12名參與反送中抗爭有案在身的港人，8月23日乘船偷渡台灣期間，被中國海警截獲拘捕，關押在深圳鹽田看守所，至昨日踏入100日。約10名身着黑衣黑帽的在台港人，昨晚7時許在捷運西門站6號出口外，舉出「SAVE 12」的燈牌，揮舞旗幟，呼籲中共釋放12港人。<br />\n<br />\n他們之後轉移陣地到西門町商圈內，向途人派發解釋事件的明信片。不少途人駐足拍照，有人在便利貼上留下聲援字句，貼在一艘象徵12港人乘坐船隻的紙船上。聲援活動半小時內快閃結束，參與的港人全程低調不受訪。香港前晚也有一群人登上獅子山望夫石，舉出一樣的燈牌聲援12名被捕者。<br />\n<br />\n12名港人被拘押至今，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"4d1e86345eeb07888eff798949c8da780c01c831","tid":2307224,"uid":148756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"台灣人真係好有香港人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729d1e253ba819386f65e56cf07a848fad8bcd26","tid":2307224,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:21:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5183c90f80c700c21fe5f170418ac044bdd6382","tid":2307224,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"74805ab4340851cb7206008a8b8fe33232185645","tid":2307224,"uid":225192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"最相近既國家 台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e686d53aa39645d8b27afeae54bdd16b63cfad","tid":2307224,"uid":7137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f980b3748a861b94361e729ed81c4aa16a865978","tid":2307224,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f4fd6156075f555e52b8eda1a88c31f4cac3bf","tid":2307224,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d1e86345eeb07888eff798949c8da780c01c831","tid":2307224,"uid":148756,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:19:01.000Z","msg":"台灣人真係好有香港人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T07:17:18.000Z","msg":"香港人黎= ="},{"pid":"8d3daea8f837413cb2d85b688ac9824500dd9123","tid":2307224,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-0